Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be in the middle of a deal since you've come at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Need a certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you become a merchant who'll intimidate his clientele by name alone in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My thoughts exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, would you happen to know anyone who'd like to travel to Lamtra?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, it seems like everyone here falls for the same trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dazzled by a certain young shepherdess, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the only person who wanders that area unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I have to tell you what the Church thinks about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't involve yourself with her if you don't want to find yourself in a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Norah the Fairy does seem to be your type of girl, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do I make the certificate out to? Or should I leave it blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it out to Lemerio Trading, please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have a buyer... Did you purchase on credit or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Is that a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did any major price fluctuations occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no reason to worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you of all people will be able to turn it to your advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and wait a bit before letting any pretty girls ensnare you, y'hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll soak up all your profits just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't invest if I didn't anticipate returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha! Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wish me lots of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:09.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\fscx105\fs80\fnMailart Rubberstamp\c&H7A8995&\pos(640,458)}Wolf and Conspiracies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They were precious. Called me a pretty little snowdrop, they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no different from hungry dogs. Don't bother with them or they might take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm kidnapped, you'll just have to rescue me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, in the end, I was the one who rescued you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know what kind of return you're expecting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but go ahead and invest to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you liked blondes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:54.22,Default,,1,1,0,,Are you attracted to her scrawny appearance? Or do you like the way her cares are etched on her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you just have a thing for shepherdesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:04:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second! He and I were just shooting the breeze. I'm not—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, sure, I thought Norah was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say our conversation wasn't fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean I don't care about you, or—well, it doesn't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I was just trying to tease you a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to take it so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,males simply say whatever's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man of my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:56.05,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,I know that knights entrust their shields and swords as proof of sincerity.{entrust?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you entrust to me as a merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll prove my sincerity to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you peaches preserved in honey—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What will you buy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that! You're crossing the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You said I should ask more charmingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you should ask nicely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to use your feminine wiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you think I was cute, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:31.08,Default,,1,1,0,,My heart was racing more from your reaction than from worrying about whether my scheme would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, now. Don't be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy to hear you say that, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you angry all the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'm not upset, okay? I'm not upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't do to get separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, losing sight of you would cause problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, business is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to use your head in order to make money,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you go too far and your plans fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll end up like Latparon Trading and be forced to sell goods at half the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do it right,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you could make huge profits with something simple, like moving armor on margin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the essence of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact that you're in debt doesn't sit well with me, even if it is temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about buying on credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:38.99,Default,,1,1,0,,You bought a hundred Lumione worth of armor at half price, which means you're in debt to Latparon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:46.34,Default,,1,1,0,,Yeah, I'll sell them to Lemerio Trading at market price, and\Nmy debt will be settled between the two trading companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:51.01,Default,,1,1,0,,I'm dealing with double my net worth, so the profit I make will be double what it would normally be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it worth the worry even if you're not fond of the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this place run by a friar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be hearing the sound of prayers if that were the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you can't hear a thing over the sound of chewing my meat pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a fine sense of wry humor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but for the sake of my reputation, I'll tell you that I can hear the sound of someone in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. But the atmosphere's unpleasant,\Nand it's definitely not lively in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hesitating won't get me anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't make money if we don't sell the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And a meat pie's no good unless you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was saving that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? If you wanted some, you should have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still some time left before the sabbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something unusual happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just arrive today, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I came here a few days ago.\NYou know how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that you're rather popular, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Craft Lawrence{*Craft Lawrence-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that you've brought armor from Latparon Trading with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we were notified by a messenger on horseback.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Latparon Trading assigned the debt to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They transferred the debt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your companion has failed miserably at business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The armor market crashed a while ago, and it's worth almost nothing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Latparon let him borrow money towards worthless stock and transferred the rights to our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Long story short, your companion was left with only his monstrous debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he's bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was tricked...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We both live by such agreements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, {*}Mr. Lemerio{*Lemerio-san}. I'm a merchant, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}, you purchased one hundred Lumione worth of arms from Latparon Trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of that, forty-seven and three-fourths Lumione was financed with debt—and a due date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I request immediate payment of your financial obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have to ask the Lohen Trading Union to assume your debt if you cannot pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the deadline for payment is the day after tomorrow, so we'll wait two days
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to return the forty-seven and 3/4 Lumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find a way to sell the armor for a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle the balance in two days. Will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to let you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we do have open air vendors at every town gate that can certainly fulfill any of your needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not hesitate to make use of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the offer, but I think I'll respectfully decline
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,since you'll probably be busy enough with other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing you in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,May God be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain what happened in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, the merchandise we're carrying has turned into scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I suppose I didn't hear wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This could mean bankruptcy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we run?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The information networks among merchants are like the eyes of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tried to do business anywhere, I'd be found out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never be able to work as a merchant again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:36.91,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,But wounded animals are eaten to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you accept that fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said I'd do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to return forty-seven Lumione gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be too difficult to make ends meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Holo, the wise wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll certainly help in any way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You could help me a great deal by cutting back on the amount you eat every—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I said all along I'd pay for my own food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can joke, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If worse comes to worst, upon my honor, I will help you escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I must use the power within the wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to take me to the northern woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have you getting tripped up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep that promise, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes to it, I may need saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop by the trading house for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me at the inn—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:42.81,Default,,1,1,0,,Do I look like the kind of ungrateful wolf that would groom her tail and let her companion face a crisis alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look like that kind of wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what {\i1}is{\i0} the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The trading house is like home for us merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what bringing a girl home means, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you simply explain the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know what to do if they reported you to the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, just tell them we're lovers or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more quick-witted than I am anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell them that you're a business associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to say anything beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That bunch can give a rough welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, I want to know who this lovely lady might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a business partner. We're traveling together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Business?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She single-handedly increased the value of my marten furs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,from 140 to 210 Trenni coins at the Milone Trading in Pazzio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did say this morning that I'd see a return from investing in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pairs like you show up ever so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The scriptures say not to carelessly open a mysterious box.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the main topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:27.63,Default,,1,1,0,,A man from Lemerio Trading just came to talk to us about\Nassuming your debt, so I have a general idea of what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, you got greedy and had the rug pulled out from under you, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes things rather simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You yourself must pay back the debt that this guild, in all likelihood, will be faced with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were swindled, robbed, or suffered losses due to illness or injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then upon our honor, we would have helped you. But not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who can save you is God—or this beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I'm not in a position where I can show you any compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I know the need to be strict at times like this that I get to stay in that gathering hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Union's laws bind us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be as upset as anyone if a member were treated as an exception to the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Loans among Union members aren't allowed, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your obligation comes due in two days, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemerio is burdened by their own failed armor investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't hesitate to demand payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, your failure will be made public the day after tomorrow, and I'll have to detain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think will happen at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be a future for me unless I come up with forty-seven Lumione within two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that you won't have a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a fate that awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will be one that is black, bitter, and heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You could pay back a debt of forty-seven Lumione in ten years by rowing a long-distance ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You could also work in a mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're lucky enough to survive that long, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A nightmare come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to see you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sins must be punished. It's my duty to enforce that simple principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you can in the next two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need my help with business, I'll do whatever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go out there and give it your best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find a way to manage in two days, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:45.10,Default,,1,1,0,,There are always possibilities in business—and some you can only see when you are in true danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you'd like to say or ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should start thinking about what to say when I repay my debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can still talk like that, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty-seven Lumione in two days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll divide the debt into smaller debts for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have people you can borrow from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a businessman, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:51.56,Default,,1,1,0,,I don't know anyone who'll lend me a substantial amount of money, but I do know a lot of people I could ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be easy if you can find forty-seven people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, {*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}. Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you brought me talk of profit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've barely started. There are still plenty of people I can ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I'm stretched pretty thin at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Prices for wheat and meat will increase as we head into the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How did things go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stock items for the upcoming spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Why? Why did I make that deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What about there? No, that's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait. Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:20:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't walk as fast as I'd like to in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, {*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for coming after the market has closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you've been making requests all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because the armor market has crashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a mistake due to my lack of foresight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lack of foresight? That might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the only one who can predict the prices of commodities, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be cruel to criticize someone on that alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}, I've had many opportunities to make money thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thought about helping you out if there was ever a time you were in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:48.91,Default,,1,1,0,,But you don't seem like a man who diligently lives according\Nto the teachings of God or is earnestly seeking relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:21:01.78,Default,,1,1,0,,You have the audacity to come with a girl in tow at a time you're desperately relying on people's goodwill?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Don't just wander into the middle of the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the inn and—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,15,,{\i1}Next Episode, "Wolf and the Grand Scheme."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:49.99,Default,,0,0,15,,{\i1}Next Episode, "Wolf and the Grand Scheme."
